            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Historical excellent school, every house one person is there from Pollocks. Late Mrs.Vijaya Lakshmi's vision & standards were taken forward successfully by Mr. Sandeep Chitra & Mrs. Rajani Chitra. Congratulations to both of them for the wonderful celebration of a successful 58 years.\n\nI'm so proud my daughter is part of Pollock's family. Recently they celebrated their annual day celebration very successfully.\n\nEspecially the team of Pollocks ( from security to class teachers, coordinators, students caretakers everyone ) did an excellent job.\n\nNOT EASY TO HANDLE THIS MANY STUDENTS IN ONE STAGE. EVERY TEACHER TAKING SPECIAL CARE OF INDIVIDUAL OF EVERY STUDENT.\n\nHAT'S OFF TO THE POLLOCK TEAM.\n\nKEEP GOING LATE VIJAYA LAKSHMI MADAM DREAM COME TRUE.\n\nITS A REAL SUCCESS OF POLLOCKS.\n\nKUDOS TO THE POLLOCK FAMILY.",
          "publisher": {
